Replace null values for price and quantity with 0
Extract discount amount from the discount_allocations array (previously extracted from the line_items field)
Discount amount is defined as the maximum value of allocated discount amount for each line item
Extract tax info from the line_item_tax_lines array (previously extracted from the line_items field)
EXTRACTING TAX DATA
Line item tax amount and tax rate are defined as the maximum value of allocated discount amount for each line item
Join discount info back with main table

Extract refunds info form the refunds column
Extract line item level refund info from the refund_line_item array (previously extracted from the refunds field)

Calculate the total refunded amount at order level
Join line items refund data back with main table
Calculate tot line item quantity after refund at order level (leaving the table at line item level)
Calculate the wight of line item quantity after with respect to the total line item quantity after refund for the whole order
Join order level refund info with line item level data
Calculate line item refund amount
The refund amount allocated to each line item is equal to the total refunded amount for the orders * the share of the line item quantity with respect to the tot line item quantity for the order
Calculate revenue values
